Developer Terms of Use
des:
Sleep Well is the Alexa skill that offers guided sessions to help you relax and drift peacefully into restful sleep. With over 10 unique sessions and a variety of soothing voices paired with calming background sounds, this skill is designed to prepare your mind and body for deep, restorative rest.

⭐ PREMIUM FEATURES ⭐ 

• Guided sessions with professional, calming voices
• A selection of background sounds ideal for relaxation and sleep
• Unlimited access with no restrictions
• Regularly updated programs to enhance your sleep meditation practice
• Full access to all session lengths

We value your feedback to help us improve and provide the best sleep and relaxation experience.

Enjoy your journey to peaceful sleep!
